(10, '2012-04-11 13:54:05', '2012-04-25 19:26:08', 'Jouons à cache cache avec Symfony2', 'Où comment gérer le manifest avec symfony2', '<p>Comment mettre en cache un site mobile en utilsant l''attribut manifest du HTML5 ?</p>\r\n<h2>Le manifest c''est quoi ?&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p>En voil&agrave; une balise pratique, il existe de tr&egrave;s bon tutoriel sur ce qu''est cette nouvelle balise <a href="http://www.html5-css3.fr/html5/tutoriel-application-web-offline-html5-cache-manifest" target="_blank">ici</a>. Mais pour r&eacute;sumer il s''agit d''un lien vers un fichier qui contient toute les routes que l''on souhaite mettre en cache o&ugrave; pas !&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Controler du manifest</h2>\r\n<p>Tout d''abbord nous allons mettre un controler qui genera le fichier manifest automatiquement. On va lui mettre une route et on va appeller les objets pour lequels on souhaite modifier les routes. Autre point important il faudra pr&eacute;ciser dans le header de la r&eacute;ponse que le type text/manifest. Sans cela les mobiles ne le reconna&icirc;trons pas comme un cache (Mais chrome si, ce qui m''a fait foirer une d&eacute;mo d''ailleurs). Ci dessous&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p id="LC15" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 1em; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;"><span class="sd" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; color: #dd1144; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">/**</span></p>\r\n<p id="LC16" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 1em; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;"><span class="sd" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; color: #dd1144; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"> * @Route("manifest/", name="manifest_mobile")</span></p>\r\n<p id="LC17" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 1em; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;"><span class="sd" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; color: #dd1144; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"> * @Template()</span></p>\r\n<p id="LC18" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 1em; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;"><span class="sd" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; color: #dd1144; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"> */</span></p>\r\n<p id="LC19" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 1em; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; font-weight: bold; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">public</span> <span class="k" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; font-weight: bold; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">function</span> <span class="nf" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; color: #990000; font-weight: bold; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">buildManifestAction</span><span class="p" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">()</span></p>\r\n<p id="LC20" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 1em; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="p" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">{</span></p>\r\n<p id="LC21" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 1em; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="nv" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; color: #008080; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">$response</span> <span class="o" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; font-weight: bold; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">=</span> <span class="k" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; font-weight: bold; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">new</span> <span class="nx" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">Response</span><span class="p" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">();</span></p>\r\n<p id="LC22" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 1em; border-style: initial; border-color