"</span> <span class="na" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: #008080; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">src=</span><span class="s" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: #dd1144; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">"</span><span class="cp" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: #999999; font-weight: bold; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">{{</span> <span class="nv" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: #008080; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">asset_url</span> <span class="cp" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: #999999; font-weight: bold; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">}}</span><span class="s" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: #dd1144; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">"</span><span class="nt" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: #000080; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span></div>\r\n<div id="LC31" class="line" style="color: #333333; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="cp" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: #999999; font-weight: bold; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">{%</span> <span class="k" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-weight: bold; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">endjavascripts</span> <span class="cp" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: #999999; font-weight: bold; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">%}</span></div>\r\n<div id="LC31" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;"><span style="color: #999999;"><strong><br /></strong></span></div>\r\n<p>Voil&agrave; les filtres seront automatquement appliqu&eacute; aux fichiers.</p>\r\n<h2>Troisi&egrave;mement on compresse la sortie avec Gzip</h2>\r\n<p>Apr&egrave;s &ccedil;a se joue au niveau d''apache et du htaccess, on va utiliser le code suivant :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="LC1" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;"># Activate filter</div>\r\n<div id="LC2" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;">SetOutputFilter DEFLATE</div>\r\n<div id="LC3" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id="LC4" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;"># Some probleme with some browser</div>\r\n<div id="LC5" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;">BrowserMatch ^Mozilla/4 gzip-only-text/html</div>\r\n<div id="LC6" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;">BrowserMatch ^Mozilla/4\\.0[678] no-gzip</div>\r\n<div id="LC7" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;">BrowserMatch \\bMSIE !no-gzip !gzip-only-text/html</div>\r\n<div id="LC8" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id="LC9" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;"># Picture don''t need to be compress</div>\r\n<div id="LC10" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;">SetEnvIfNoCase Request_URI \\.(?:gif|jpe?g|png)$ no-gzip dont-vary</div>\r\n<div id="LC11" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id="LC12" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;"># Pour les proxy</div>\r\n<div id="LC13" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;">Header append Vary User-Agent env=!dont-vary</div>\r\n<div id="LC13" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>Bien &eacute;videmment pour que cel&agrave; fonctionne il faut que le navigateur du client supporte la compression mais rassurez vous tous les "bons" navigateurs le supportent.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Optimiser son autoload</h2>\r\n<p>Composer permet de g&eacute;nrer un autoload plus efficace avec la commande suivante :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.898438); color: #555555; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;">composer.phar dump-autoload --optimize</span></p>\r\n<p>Et votre autoload sera plus performant ...</p>\r\n<h2>Avec APC on partage la m&eacute;moire et le chargement ...</h2>\r\n<p>Je donne la proc&eacute;dure avec symfony 2.1 car cela fonctionne, il suffit de modifier le fichier app.php</p>\r\n<div id="LC11" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;"><span class="nv" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: #008080; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">$loader</span> <span class="o" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-weight: bold; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">=</span> <span class="k" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-weight: bold; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">new</span> <span class="nx" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">ApcClassLoader</span><span class="p" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">(</span><span class="s1" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: #dd1144; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">''fabbook''</span><span class="p" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">,</span> <span class="nv" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: #008080; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">$loader</span><span class="p" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">);</span></div>\r\n<div id="LC12" class="line" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; margin: 0px;"><span class="nv" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: #008080; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">$loader</span><span class="o" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-weight: bold; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">-&gt;</span><span class="na" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: #008080; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">register</span><span class="p" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">(</span><span class="k" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-weight: bold; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">true</span><span class="p" style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">);</span></div>\r\n<p>Remplacer ''fabbook'' par le nom de votre application et c''est bon. Bien entendu il faut que votre serveur supporte apc mais si c''est le cas alors cel&agrave; devrait encore acc&eacute;l&eacute;rer les choses.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>La touche finale : Varnish c''est quand m&ecirc;me mieux</h2>\r\n<p>Bon j''aurai bien aim&eacute; pouvoir utiliser ce reverse proxy sur mon serveur de prod mais un ovh mutalis&eacute; ne permet pas de faire ce que l''on veut. Ceci dit tous les m&eacute;canismes de mise en cache que l''on aura mis en place seront valide avec varnish.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Conclusion&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p>Le contact avec le collegue fut finalement profitable car cel&agrave; m''a pouss&eacute; &agrave; me poser des questions et &agrave; trouver des solutions techniques plus satisfaisantes que <em>"echo est plus rapide que print"</em>&nbsp;<em>&nbsp;</em>et finalement la vrai question que l''on doit se poser c''est comment faire en sorte de solliciter mon application le moins possible ? J''esp&egrave;re que cet article vous sera utilie et si vous avez d''autres id&eacute;es n''h&eacute;sitez pas &agrave; vous manifester.&nbsp;</p>', 'optimiser-son-site-symfony2-pour-la-performance', 2, 1, 1);
